channel.title: Project unknown dev team. Client has all skill capes and such! [RECRUITING]
channel.description:
The aim of this server is to have all skills working decent so that people can enjoy it.
The client.java file is currently: 309kb
There is a handler for every skill added apart from 1 (will do it soon)
LATEST UPDATE: Saradomin sword added. New gfx to go with it. Moving lightning :d
This is the rs gfx i screenied mine at the wrong time >> [IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/saradomin_sword.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/sarasword.jpg[/img]
Well, heres a little look at the client. NOTE: This is not upto-date this is one i released a few days ago
FORUMS: [url=http://www.projectunknown.co.nr]HERE[/url] >> Please register if you would like to become a Project unknown member or coder.
For more information also check the server guide on the forums: Not complete because im adding alot of pictures and need to add all skills only done like 4 on it at the moment.
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/newupdated.jpg[/img]
This server is already very developed by me with almost all skills handled.
Im looking for decent members to help me finish off this project. Also a php coder maybe usefull.
[b][u]Server pictures: Note: Not all the skills[/u][/b]
[b][u]Fishing:[/u][/b]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/Project%20unknown/Fishing.jpg[/img]
[b][u]Cooking.[/b][/u]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/Project%20unknown/Fullcooking.jpg[/img]
[b][u]Crafting. Not quite finished.[/u][/b]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/Project%20unknown/crafting.jpg[/img]
[b][u]Pickpocketing - Most npc's finished.[/u][/b]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/Project%20unknown/Pickpocketing.jpg[/img]
[b][u]Fletching with interfaces![/u][/b]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/Project%20unknown/Fletching.jpg[/img]
[b][u]Woodcutting[/u][/b]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/Project%20unknown/Woodcutting.jpg[/img]
[b][u]Mining[/u][/b]
Mining picture didn't upload for some reason, ill add it later.
[SIZE=7]The following skill is my next project. Cook x! [/SIZE]
[IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u116/the_owner2007/cookingx.jpg[/img]
If you would like to become a team member then please go to the forums and post an application in the coders section
FORUMS: [url=http://www.projectunknown.co.nr]HERE[/url]
IF YOU ARE GOING TO APPLY PLEASE ALSO JUST POST SOMETHING HERE TO KEEP THIS THREAD ALIVE! [br][size=1]Posted on: September 04, 2007, 02:35:42 PM[/size][hr]Oops sorry, ment to click edit
